'''Leia d'al' Gargan''' was the [[Gender/Legends|daughter]] of [[Nautag d'al' Gargan|Nautag]] and [[Yarna d'al' Gargan/Legends|Yarna d'al' Gargan]] and sister of [[Luka d'al' Gargan]] and [[Nautag d'al' Gargan II]]. She was named after [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]].

She formed a [[Jizz/Legends|jizz]] trio with her siblings in the vein of [[Max Rebo Band/Legends|Max Rebo]].

